column5: Got into a bunch of deep water crappies((16ft),released all  then remembered to take a pic.
Nice...  If you ever need another guy in the boat....feel free to pm me...  Lol...  I wish
Another really good fish Larry. Thanks for posting.

Couple generic questions on these critters if I may??  What size lure you droppin to 16 ft  What was the water temp?  And do they appear as baitfish on your screen----also are they in some sort of cover--or just on a flat  Reason I ask this---Apparently crappie are in a nearby lake ---big and deep  I'm tryin lots with zip success---I've never been a crappie angler all this time---just learnin
